race.description: Sportsbet Supporters Of Having A Crack
race.comment: HILLBILLY LEXI (7) struggled to get involved last start at Bendigo, but prior to that won comfortably by 4 lengths at this track (25.88) beating Aston Joe in a Grade 6 on September 19. Has ability and is a key runner. SMOOTH PRINCE (6) has a strong record here with three wins and a minor from five starts. Was out of placings last time (29.53) at Sale in a Grade 5, finishing fourth and beaten 2.25 lengths. Looks suited here and can measure up. BUSH LASS (2) drew the squeeze box and managed to fill the frame when second (26.08) at Warrnambool in Grade 5. Missed the placings only try here. Can feature again. PAW JULIA (3) cannot be ruled out.
